<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uelaurieldragonstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elauriel Dragonstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Mistress Elauriel</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/9/02 11:03:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1963.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> The epic shield (800 point rune) has radically changed the way I play.  Your role can be redefined (at least in some situations) one you obtain your epic.  It's uses are many and always wonderful.<br>
<br>
1.  I can pull for AoE groups.  This is especially true in HS where the harm touches can be absorbed by my shield (as long as there aren't too many of them)<br>
<br>
2.  I can tank sometimes when necessary in xp situations.  I do this often when duoing with a ranger or rogue.  Rogue can backstab after I nuke, til he builds up enough aggro, then I nuke again.<br>
<br>
3.  High end mobs almost always seem to cast an AoE.  I don't take damage, and can recast it when possible (usually easy to do), thus saving the clerics mana for tanks who need it.<br>
<br>
4.  I can be more aggressive with the nuking in xp groups, especially if we need things dead in a hurry.<br>
<br>
Our epic effect is one of the absolute best out there in my opinion.  I know I am not alone in that thinking as well. <p><img src ="http://web4.facelink.com/edit/raw/rawimage/86/2369886.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=1963.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=1963.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1963.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=1963.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1963.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1963.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1963.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1